## Main Options

| Option             | Meaning                                                             |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `--tickers`        | Comma-separated list of tickers                                     |
| `--watchlist`      | CSV file with tickers                                               |
| `--mode`           | Strategy mode: `aggressive`, `balanced`, `conservative`, `dividend` |
| `--top-n`          | Number of top stocks to select                                      |
| `--objective`      | Optimization objective: `sharpe`, `minvar`, `risk_parity`           |
| `--history-period` | yfinance history period, for example `1y`, `3y`, `5y`               |
| `--lookback-days`  | Lookback period for scoring                                         |
| `--min-marketcap`  | Minimum market cap filter                                           |
| `--min-volume`     | Minimum average volume filter                                       |
| `--no-news`        | Disable news scoring                                                |
| `--gpu`            | Use optional GPU covariance calculation                             |
| `--workers`        | Number of parallel workers                                          |

